@startuml svc-check-in--post-check-ins-check_in_id-gear-verification

!include ../theme.puml
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #2563eb
}

header [[/microservices/svc-check-in/#integration-context ⬆ svc-check-in Integration Context]]

title POST /check-ins/{check_in_id}/gear-verification\nVerify adventure gear\n<size:10><color:#7c3aed>ARCHITECT OVERRIDE — enriched with safety-grade verification and inventory binding</color></size>

participant "Ops Staff" as Client [[/actors/#operations-staff]]
participant "svc-check-in" as Svc [[/microservices/svc-check-in/]] #DBEAFE
participant "Gear Inventory" as GI [[/microservices/svc-gear-inventory/]] #CFFAFE
participant "Safety" as Safety [[/microservices/svc-safety-compliance/]] #FEE2E2
database "PostgreSQL" as DB [[/microservices/svc-check-in/#data-store]] #FEF9C3

note over Svc
  [[/services/api/svc-check-in.html View in Swagger UI]]
end note

Client -> Svc : POST /check-ins/{id}/gear-verification\n{ gear_items[], inspector_id }
activate Svc #2563eb

Svc -> DB : SELECT * FROM check_ins\nWHERE id = check_in_id
activate DB #FEF9C3
DB --> Svc : Check-in record\n(adventure_type, pattern,\nguest_id)
deactivate DB

Svc -> GI : [[/microservices/svc-gear-inventory/#get-gear-items-list-gear-inventory GET /gear-items]]\nVerify all required items\nfor adventure pattern
activate GI #CFFAFE
GI --> Svc : Gear catalog match\n(required[], condition[])
deactivate GI

note right of Svc : Gear checklist evaluation:\n- All required items present?\n- Condition grade ≥ minimum?\n- Certifications current?\n(Pattern 2/3 require\ncertified safety gear)

alt Any gear fails inspection
    Svc -> DB : UPDATE check_ins\nSET gear_status = FAILED,\nfailed_items = [...]
    activate DB #FEF9C3
    DB --> Svc : Updated
    deactivate DB

    Svc --> Client : 200 OK\n(status = FAILED,\nfailed_items[], next_steps)
    deactivate Svc
else All gear passes
    Svc -> Safety : [[/microservices/svc-safety-compliance/#get-waivers-list-waivers Validate waiver coverage]]\nfor high-risk gear
    activate Safety #FEE2E2
    Safety --> Svc : Waiver status\n(all_signed: true/false)
    deactivate Safety

    Svc -> DB : UPDATE check_ins\nSET gear_status = VERIFIED,\nverified_by = inspector_id,\nverified_at = NOW()
    activate DB #FEF9C3
    DB --> Svc : Updated
    deactivate DB

    Svc --> Client : 200 OK\n(status = VERIFIED,\ngear_items[], verified_at)
    deactivate Svc
end

@enduml
